article_title: Eight-Year-Old Killed in Quitman Car Accident
article_text:
An eight-year-old girl was killed in a one-vehicle accident in Quitman Saturday morning.

The Mississippi Highway Patrol says four people were in the car traveling southbound on Hwy 513. The car ran off the road and collided with a tree. Highway patrol says eight-year-old Marveanna Tillman was ejected from the car and died from her injuries.

Clarke County Hot Topics provides this picture from the scene.
